是十重态部分拉氏量中的一个参数，
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Theta^{\mu\nu}=g^{\mu\nu}-\left(Z+\frac{1}{2}\right)\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}
\]

\end_inset

我们最后会取
\begin_inset Formula $Z=\frac{1}{2}$
\end_inset

，所以
\begin_inset Formula $\Theta^{\mu\nu}=g^{\mu\nu}-\left(Z+\frac{1}{2}\right)\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}=g^{\mu\nu}-\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}=-\frac{1}{2}\left(\gamma^{\mu}\gamma^{\nu}-\gamma^{\nu}\gamma^{\mu}\right)=i\sigma^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

。
\begin_inset Newline newline
\end_inset

如果
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi}$
\end_inset

是旋量，
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi}\sigma^{\mu\nu}\psi$
\end_inset

是厄米的。一般来说，如果
\begin_inset Formula $A_{\mu\nu}^{\dagger}=A_{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\left(\bar{\psi}\sigma^{\mu\nu}\psi A_{\mu\nu}\right)^{\dagger}=A_{\mu\nu}^{\dagger}\psi^{\dagger}\left(-\frac{i}{2}\left(\gamma^{\nu\dagger}\gamma^{\mu\dagger}-\gamma^{\mu\dagger}\gamma^{\nu\dagger}\right)\right)\gamma^{0}\psi=\bar{\psi}\sigma^{\mu\nu}\psi A_{\mu\nu}
\]

\end_inset

所以
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{\psi}\Theta^{\mu\nu}\psi$
\end_inset

不是厄米的，它在厄米共轭下出一项负号。或者利用
\begin_inset Formula $\Theta^{\mu\nu}$
\end_inset

对于指标是反对称的，把这个负号囊括进交换指标顺序
\begin_inset Formula $\Theta^{\mu\nu}\to\Theta^{\nu\mu}$
\end_inset

，salamu 文章中即是如此。
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
 & \mathcal{C}\left[\varepsilon^{ijk}\overline{T}_{\mu}^{ilm}\Theta^{\mu\nu}\left(u_{\nu}\right)^{lj}B^{mk}+\text{h.c.}\right]\\
\sim & \frac{C_{T\phi}}{f}\bar{T}_{\rho}\left(x\right)\partial_{\sigma}\phi\left(x\right)\Theta^{\rho\sigma}p\left(x\right)+\frac{C_{T\phi}}{f}\bar{p}\left(x\right)\Theta^{\alpha\beta}T_{\beta}\left(x\right)\partial_{\alpha}\phi\left(x\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

